---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config/siteConfig';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about AI Tools Review and our mission to help you find the best AI tools."
>
  <Navigation />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h1>About {siteConfig.name}</h1>

      <p>
        Welcome to {siteConfig.name}, your trusted source for in-depth reviews and comparisons
        of the latest AI tools. Our mission is to help you make informed decisions when choosing
        AI tools for your personal or business needs.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        The AI tool landscape is evolving rapidly. Every day, new tools Launch with promises of
        revolutionizing how we work, create, and communicate. But with so many options available,
        it can be overwhelming to find the right tool for your specific needs.
      </p>
      <p>
        We exist to cut through the noise and provide honest, detailed reviews that help you understand:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>What each tool does and who it's best for</li>
        <li>How it compares to alternatives in the market</li>
        <li>Pricing structures and value for money</li>
        <li>Key features and limitations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Review Process</h2>
      <p>
        Every review we publish follows a rigorous process:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Hands-on testing:</strong> We use each tool extensively to understand its capabilities</li>
        <li><strong>Feature comparison:</strong> We compare features against competitors</li>
        <li><strong>Pricing analysis:</strong> We break down pricing and value</li>
        <li><strong>User feedback:</strong> We consider real user experiences</li>
        <li><strong>Regular updates:</strong> We revisit reviews to keep them current</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>E-E-A-T Principles</h2>
      <p>
        We follow Google's E-E-A-T (Experience, Expertise, Authoritativeness, Trustworthiness) guidelines:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Experience:</strong> We actually use the tools we review</li>
        <li><strong>Expertise:</strong> Our team has deep knowledge of AI and technology</li>
        <li><strong>Authoritativeness:</strong> We cite sources and provide verifiable claims</li>
        <li><strong>Trustworthiness:</strong> We disclose affiliations and maintain editorial independence</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have a tool you'd like us to review? Questions about our methodology?
        Reach out at <a href="mailto:contact@aitools.pages.dev">{siteConfig.author.email}</a>
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>